  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/58b6a6c5967f9435207e0a36198ba03a.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/58b6a6c5967f9435207e0a36198ba03a.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/58b6a6c5967f9435207e0a36198ba03a.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ EXPLORE</strong></h2> The remains of an alien world concealing as many <strong>secrets areas</strong> and <strong>puzzles</strong> as <strong>traps</strong> and <strong>sneaky creatures</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/fdc38c80de8d60e19a3d780b4b5ff1e8.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/fdc38c80de8d60e19a3d780b4b5ff1e8.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/fdc38c80de8d60e19a3d780b4b5ff1e8.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ BE TRICKY </strong></h2> Using your items cleverly to fight and solve puzzles. Use the landscape elements to <strong>hide</strong> and <strong>one-shot mobs</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/646bb17a60ed49265d8281d57d2c6095.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/646bb17a60ed49265d8281d57d2c6095.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/646bb17a60ed49265d8281d57d2c6095.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ BATTLE</strong></h2> Challenging bosses to the beat of an <strong>electro-dark</strong> soundtrack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/a2a33e7a1a9b6fdfa837e0eeca711b5e.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/a2a33e7a1a9b6fdfa837e0eeca711b5e.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/a2a33e7a1a9b6fdfa837e0eeca711b5e.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ SKILLS SANCTUARY </strong></h2> <strong>Collect experience points</strong> by defeating creatures, finding chests and more.<br><br>Spend them to <strong>unlock new abilities</strong> (Explosive Arrows, improve your run speed etc.) or <strong>buy ammo</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/d576ca9da9d7ab830bde4a1b52a5f3e6.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/d576ca9da9d7ab830bde4a1b52a5f3e6.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/d576ca9da9d7ab830bde4a1b52a5f3e6.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ DIE AND RETRY</strong></h2><br>Sacrificing a few ammunition along the way...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/bb6fb6cbdb31a0f61756900f0dedaf6d.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/bb6fb6cbdb31a0f61756900f0dedaf6d.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/bb6fb6cbdb31a0f61756900f0dedaf6d.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ REACH THE SOURCE...</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/b25fc79da92452be4e8af5c93270c78b.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/b25fc79da92452be4e8af5c93270c78b.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/b25fc79da92452be4e8af5c93270c78b.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><u><strong>Features:</strong></u><br><br><i>- Dark / enigmatic atmosphere.<br>- 2 difficulty modes (Normal / Cursed).<br>- 18 skills to unlock / earn.<br>- Challenging bosses.<br>- About 10 hours of play.</i>",
